Bulk Free Packaging: Pacifiers come in a sealed plastic poly bag to reduce waste", "description": "NUK Comfy Pacifiers feature a one-piece, 100% silicone design that gently contours to baby's face. The heart-shaped shield fits perfectly under baby’s nose for easier breathing and to prevent irritation.
